Package: survey160r
Title: R Client for Survey160 Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lennon", "Shimokawa", email = "lshimokawa@survey160.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Access Survey160 campaign data from R. Currently supports
    reading campaign results directly from Google Cloud Storage into data
    frames. Survey160 API support is planned for a future release.
